question: What restaurant is there on the way to Procter Farm Preserve, Wendell, NC within 160 kilometers from Fayetteville State University, Fayetteville, NC?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.892474 35.0726)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.390009 35.831172)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.892474 35.0726)',4326)::geography, 160000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.892474 35.0726)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
